title: Dr. Kim Hunter and the Apparition

sources.title: Dr Kim Hunter and The Apparition | Full Movie | Paranormal Horror | Chaselyn Wade
sources.description:
Kim Hunter and The Apparition - A renowned celebrity medium, Dr. Kim Hunter’s star is starting to fade. Mired in press controversy, she leads a team of fellow clairvoyants that communicate with spirits. Suddenly, a person from her past comes with a case that hits home and brings her and the team back to her humble rural beginnings. She must confront the paranormal that lurks in her past while helping to rid the unwanted spirits in the present.
2022.  Stars: April Hartman, Jade Summers, Chaselyn Wade
